sec.p:
Caenorhabditis elegans strains maintenance followed the protocol from wormbook [82]. The Bristol N2 strain was used as wild-type. Males were generated through heat shock and maintained in a mixed population with hermaphrodites [83]. The following strains were employed in this study, with their detailed genotypes or microinjection mixtures described within square brackets:


GR1333, yzIs71[Ptph-1::GFP + rol-6(su1006)] V;

PSC140, scnEx92[WY079(Pnmr-1sp::loxp::STOP::loxp::HisCl1), 30ng/uL; XZ046(flp18p::Cre), 30ng/uL; CC::GFP, 30ng/uL];

PSC286, scnEx223[XZ046(flp18p::nCre), 31ng/uL; YW379(nmr1sp::loxp::Stop::loxp::nGC6s), 6ng/uL; CC::DsRed2, 39ng/uL; pUC19, 24ng/uL];

PSC138, scnEx90[YW397(Ptbh-1p::TeTx::mCherry), 30ng/uL; CC::GFP, 31ng/uL; pUC19, 30ng/uL];

PSC412, scnEx302[YW398(ceh-63p::TeTx::mCherry), 45ng/uL; CC::GFP, 30ng/uL; pUC19, 30ng/uL];

PSC227, scnEx166[YW396(gcy36p::TeTx::mCherry), 30ng/uL; CC::GFP, 30ng/uL; pUC19, 40ng/uL];

PSC132, scnEx84[YW399(Pnmr1sp-nmr1 sense), 30.6ng/uL; YW400(Pflp18p-nmr1 anti-sense), 30.4ng/uL; CC::DsRed2, 39ng/uL];

PSC136, scnEx88[YW401(Pnmr1sp-nmr2 sense), 30.1ng/uL; YW402(Pflp18p-nmr2 anti-sense), 30ng/uL; CC::DsRed2, 39ng/uL];

PSC149, scnEx101[YW405(Pflp18p-glr2 anti-sense, 30.5ng/uL; YW406(Pnmr1sp-glr2 sense), 30ng/uL; CC::GFP, 31ng/uL];

PSC233, scnEx172[YW474(Pnmr1sp-ser3-sense, 31ng/uL; YW475(Pflp18p-ser3-anti sense), 30ng/uL; CC::GFP, 40ng/uL];

PSC320, scnEx245[YW495(Pnmr1sp-ser6 sense), 33ng/uL; YW496(Pflp18p-ser6 anti-sense), 30ng/uL; CC::GFP, 30ng/uL];

PSC321, scnEx246[YW495(Pnmr1sp-ser6 sense), 33ng/uL; YW496(Pflp18p-ser6 anti-sense), 30ng/uL; CC::GFP, 30ng/uL];

BNU001, scnEx223; scnEx90 [mated by PSC286 and PSC138];

BNU002, scnEx223; scnEx302 [mated by PSC286 and PSC412];

BNU003, scnEx223; scnEx166 [mated by PSC286 and PSC227].
